---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About QSol Analytics"
  description="Data science consultancy founded by David J. McCann. Physics-trained rigour applied to business problems for UK SMEs."
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate">About QSol Analytics</h1>

      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-light">
        <p class="text-xl">
          QSol Analytics helps UK SMEs turn messy data into clear decisions and manual processes into automated workflows.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">The Founder</h2>
        <p>
          I'm David J. McCann, founder of QSol Analytics. My background is in physics—trained to find patterns in complex systems and extract signal from noise.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before starting QSol, I saw the same pattern repeatedly: businesses sitting on valuable data but struggling to extract insights. Enterprise consultancies quoted six-figure projects. Off-the-shelf tools never quite fit. Internal teams were stretched too thin.
        </p>
        <p>
          QSol Analytics exists to bridge that gap—bringing rigorous data science to SMEs at a scale and price that makes sense.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose mt-6">
          <div class="bg-brand-blue-pale p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Rapid Time-to-Value</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">From discovery call to working prototype in 2-4 weeks. No death by PowerPoint.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-blue-pale p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Signal Over Noise</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">We cut through complexity to surface what matters. Clarity, not more dashboards.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-blue-pale p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Measurable Outcomes</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">Success metrics agreed upfront. You see the ROI before the final invoice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-blue-pale p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Founder Access</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">You work directly with me, not handed to junior staff.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Who We Work With</h2>
        <p>
          We specialise in operations-heavy UK SMEs—businesses with 10-500 employees where data is plentiful but insights are scarce. Our clients typically operate in:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Logistics and distribution</li>
          <li>Manufacturing</li>
          <li>Retail and ecommerce</li>
          <li>Professional services</li>
          <li>Property and facilities management</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">The Name</h2>
        <p>
          QSol stands for "Quantitative Solutions"—a reminder that everything we do is grounded in measurable outcomes, not vague promises.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Ready to talk?"
    description="Book a free discovery call to discuss your challenges and see if we're a fit."
  />
</BaseLayout>
